data.description: Priced to sell!! This home has it all including Z Wave enabled smart switches and plugs! Offering the best of both worlds: serene surroundings and a convenient location. As you step inside, you will be greeted by wood floors and an abundance of natural light. The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen, boasting granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample storage space. The large, private backyard backs to common space and is an oasis for relaxation and play. Storage shed and 84 sprinkler head irrigation to keep your lawn looking lush. New back flow preventer and control board has 1 year transferable warranty. You'll love spending warm summer evenings on the large deck, hosting barbecues or simply enjoying the tranquility of the outdoors. Inside, the primary suite features a walk-in closet & an en-suite bathroom with double vanities, a walk-in shower, and a luxurious garden tub – The bonus room provides endless possibilities as a home office, playroom, or guest room.
